data.title: Is Chevron with Techron really the best for gas mileage?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 2): NO. I have seen no published statistics indicating fuel mileage differences between major gasoline brands. If they existed, this would be an irresistible advertising tool and claims could be easily challenged or supported.
